  <div class="comment">
    <h3 class="title"><a href="/cell-carriers-let-us-have-more-one-phone-same-number#comment-2691" class="active">but what happens if you</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="http://mobquery.com" rel="nofollow">damien</a> (not verified) on Wed, 2007-01-17 13:33.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>but what happens if you answer both cell phones at the same time? think of all the overhead in processing that the cell carriers wil have to do in order to provide a service that's marginally useful.  also, the more cell phones you have, the more likely you are to lose one. do you really need 3 cellphones when the size of the phone you have now can easily fit in your shirt-pocket?</p>
</div>
    <div class="links">&raquo; <ul class="links"><li class="first last comment_reply"><a href="/comment/reply/505/2691" class="comment_reply">reply</a></li>
