    <div class="content"><p>I take it that you continue to disagree with me as to how easy this is to implement.  So, since you believe that you're right, we can expect cellphone companies to begin to offer it this spring.  Or, if I'm right, they won't begin to offer it for several months at the earliest.</p>
<p>Want to bet on your position?</p>
</div>
